Next, using attribute rdf:about , identiÔ¨Åes the resource the statement is about (the subject of the state- ment), by providing its URI http://agh.edu.pl#Student .Line 5 declares property element agh:hasName for the subject resource, where both predicate and object of the statement are repre- sented.

2.3 Seismic observations For the analysis of the seismic characteristics, we used seismograms obtained by worldwide networks of the broadband seismic stations Iris/Ida (II, http://ida.ucsd.edu/) and Iris/USGS (IU, http://earthquake.usgs.gov/regional/asl/) and by four re- gional networks: Iris/China (IC), Kazakhstan (KZ), Kyrgyzstan (KR) and Baikal regional seismological center (BY, Russia).
